 <li><strong>Project:</strong> Joomla!</li>
 <li><strong>SubProject:</strong> plg_xstandard</li>
 <li><strong>Severity:</strong> High</li>
 <li><strong>Versions:</strong> 1.5.8 and all previous 1.5 releases</li>
 <li><strong>Exploit type:</strong> Directory Traversal</li>
 <li><strong>Reported Date:</strong> 2009-January-7</li>
 <li><strong>Fixed Date:</strong> 2009-January-9</li>
</ul>
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>A crafted request can cause disclosure of the directory structure on the server (including any directory that php has access to).</p>
<h2>Affected Installs</h2>
<p>All 1.5.x installs prior to and including 1.5.8 are affected.</p>
<h2>Solution</h2>
<p>Upgrade to latest Joomla! version (1.5.9 or newer).</p>
